    "title": "Texas Monthly Top 50 BBQ — The Bump Chart",
    "source": "Texas Monthly quadrennial Top 50 BBQ lists (2008, 2013, 2017, 2021, 2025), cross-checked against CultureMap, PaperCity, WFAA, Texas BBQ Posse, and contemporaneous reporting.",
    "notes": "rank is present only when the published edition ranked that position. 2013 ranked only a top 4 (Franklin #1; the other three listed alphabetically). 2008 published a full ranked list but only Snow's #1 is reliably recoverable from free sources — others omitted rather than guessed."
